<hr />

<p>VS Code doesnâ€™t come with the same layout by default. Itâ€™s for the better and you can have the same Atom-like workflow in VS Code. Just enable a Secondary Side Bar and drag your â€œSource Controlâ€ and â€œCommitsâ€ to the second pane.</p>

